  <data name="Secret.Desc" xml:space="preserve"><value>A secret is a named key (for example ConnectionStrings:Main) that can hold a different encrypted value in each environment. Choose View to see or set its per-environment values, or Delete… to open it and remove it. Every change is saved as a new encrypted version, so earlier values are never silently overwritten.</value></data>
