  <data name="Token.Issue.Desc" xml:space="preserve"><value>Issue one token per application and environment. Give it a clear name (which app or service it belongs to), an optional note (where it runs, owner, ticket) and an optional expiry after which it stops working. Scoping each token to a single environment keeps the blast radius small if one ever leaks.</value></data>
