  <data name="Token.Existing.Desc" xml:space="preserve"><value>Each token is listed with its prefix (the visible start of the value, to identify it), creation date, expiry and status. Edit changes its name and note; Rotate issues a fresh secret value for the same token and immediately invalidates the old one (use it on a schedule or after a suspected leak); Revoke permanently disables it.</value></data>
